[It is for exactly this reason that support of the countries in Africa affected by Ebola must be maintained by the global community. It is equally important to increase support of basic and applied research, even during times when we don't have overt outbreaks of disease. As data sources have now improved for Ebola, it is hoped reliable predictions are now being made. - Roger Feldman & Mod.LK]

